$k_t$ against uncorrelated\nthermal background, thus confirming this observable as a potential candidate to\nunveil medium dynamics around the dead cone regime.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2022 19:00:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 20 Mar 2023 19:52:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-17"}
