\ninsight into the potential future consideration of analytical solutions in\nfuture NeRF extensions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Nov 2022 13:56:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 25 Mar 2023 20:29:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-28"}
